  * Comprehensive test suite and CI/CD pipeline

 -- SLURM Exporter Team <maintainers@slurm-exporter.io>  Thu, 14 Dec 2023 15:30:00 +0000

slurm-exporter (0.8.0-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Alpha release with basic SLURM metrics collection
  * Support for jobs, nodes, and partitions collectors
  * RESTful API integration with SLURM controller
  * Basic authentication and configuration management
  * Initial documentation and installation guides

